                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </el-disclosure>
                </div>
                <div class="py-6 first:pt-0 last:pb-0">
                  <div>
                    <button
                      type="button"
                      data-command="--toggle"
                      data-commandfor="faq-5"
                      aria-label="Toggle answer for: What are your store hours and location?"
                      class="flex w-full items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900 hover:cursor-pointer"
                    >
                      <span class="text-base/7 font-semibold"
                        >What are your store hours and location?</span
                      >
                      <span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center">
                        <svg
                          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                          fill="none"
                          stroke="currentColor"
                          stroke-width="1.5"
                          data-slot="icon"
                          aria-hidden="true"
